{{> layout/header}}
<style>
    body {
        background-color: #fff;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }
    .profile-card {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: left;
    }
    .profile-card img {
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #ddd;
    }
    .profile-card .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .profile-card .header .info {
        margin-left: 20px;
    }
    .profile-card .header .info h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .profile-card .header .info p {
        margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .profile-card .points, .profile-card .vip-points {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .profile-card .points h4, .profile-card .vip-points h4 {
        font-weight: bold;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .profile-card .points p, .profile-card .vip-points p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .profile-card .grid {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .profile-card .grid div {
        flex: 1;
        margin: 0 5px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        height: 100px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
    }
    .profile-card .grid .setting {
        background-color: #343a40;
        color: white;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .sidebar {
        border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding-right: 20px;
    }
    .sidebar h5 {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .sidebar ul {
        padding-left: 0;
        list-style: none;
    }
    .sidebar ul li {
        padding: 10px 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .sidebar ul li:hover {
        color: #007bff;
    }
    .content-section {
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .content-section h5 {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content-section .row div {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .content-section .row div:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .content-section .row div h6 {
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content-section p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #6c757d;
    }

    .boxed {
        border: 1px solid #ddd; /* 테두리 설정 */
        padding: 20px; /* 내용물과 테두리 사이의 여백 */
        border-radius: 5px; /* 모서리 둥글게 */
        background-color: #f9f9f9; /* 배경색 설정 */
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* + 버튼 */
    .add-button {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 24px; /* 크기 조정 */
        height: 24px; /* 크기 조정 */
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 50%;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 22px; /* 중앙 정렬 */
        margin-left: 10px;
        cursor: pointer;
        background-color: #f4f4f4; /* 배경색 추가 */
        color: #333; /* 글자색 설정 */
        font-weight: bold; /* 글자 두껍게 */
        transition: background-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; /* 부드러운 전환 효과 */
    }

    .add-button:hover {
        background-color: #ddd; /* 호버 시 배경색 변경 */
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* 호버 시 그림자 추가 */
    }

</style>

<div class="container">
    <div class="profile-card">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="profile picture">
            <div class="info">
                <h3>박찬혁님</h3>
                <p><strong>cowtti97</strong></p>
                <p>고객님은 <span class="text-danger">일반</span> 입니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 points">
                <h4>POINT <span><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></h4>
                <p>사용가능 포인트 <strong>300 점</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 vip-points">
                <h4>VIP 점수 <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i></h4>
                <p>VIP 누적 점수 <strong>300/10,000점</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <div>1</div>
            <div>2</div>
            <div>3</div>
            <div>4</div>
            <div>5</div>
            <div class="setting" style="text-align: center;">자주가는 극장 설정하기</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 밑의 부분 -->
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-3 sidebar">

            <ul>
                <li><h5>MY HOME</h5></li>
                <li>나의 예매내역</li>
                <li>회원정보</li>
                <li style="margin-left: 10%;">회원정보 수정</li>
                <li style="margin-left: 10%;">회원탈퇴</li>
                <li>나의 문의내역</li>
                <li style="margin-left: 10%;">1:1 문의</li>
                <li style="margin-left: 10%;">분실물 문의</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-9 content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="icon">
                    <h6>기대되는 영화</h6>
                    <p>보고 싶은 영화를<br>미리 담아두고 싶다면?</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="icon">
                    <h6>내가 본 영화</h6>
                    <p>관람한 영화를<br>한 번에 모아 보고 싶다면?</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="icon">
                    <h6>내가 쓴 평점</h6>
                    <p>관람 후 내 느낌을<br>점수로 남기고 싶다면?</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <br>

            <div class="mt-4">
                <h5>MY 예매내역 0건 <span class="add-button">+</span></h5>
                <div class="mt-4 boxed">
                    <p>고객님의 최근 예매내역이 존재하지 않습니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <h5>MY Q&A 0건 <span class="add-button">+</span></h5>
                <div class="mt-4 boxed">
                    <p>고객님의 1:1 문의내역이 존재하지 않습니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

